heading: Contrabass flute music.
general-note: Here are entered compositions not in a specific form or of a specific type for solo contrabass flute, and collections of compositions in several forms or types for solo contrabass flute..

The term "contrabass flute" is used as a medium of performance in headings for works for one or two solo instruments. In headings for other works that include contrabass flute, the generic term "flute" is used as the medium of performance..
